{"tid":99104,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【包括20中國客】載31人船隻昨赴沙巴途中失聯 搜索至今未有發現","createTime":"2017-01-29T02:57:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-29T06:28:40.000Z","uid":42188,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0d5277ff1607387856ce1f26d916e6631f370128","tid":99104,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T02:57:36.000Z","msg":"中國駐馬來西亞亞庇（沙巴州首府）總領事館周日證實，一艘載有31人、包括約20名中國遊客的船隻，周六由亞庇前往沙巴環灘島途中失去聯絡。當局目前仍在搜索，但截至今早9時仍未有發現。<br />\n<br />\n總領事館表示，昨已聯絡當地旅遊文化及環境部長證實消息，並要求協助派人全力搜救。目前由大馬海軍和海警局聯合組成的搜救隊，正在相關海域展開搜索。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"788da2eda519963a482eff1707ee1682541aa05e","tid":99104,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T03:01:02.000Z","msg":"熱烈彈琴"},{"pid":"1190c448a40b9f91bb510d7c64492cc04e5beeee","tid":99104,"uid":20658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T03:02:28.000Z","msg":"新年放佢一馬啦"},{"pid":"d0a74e72ff9132a8fa4eb1fbb2cf9a9b1a1b477d","tid":99104,"uid":24781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T03:04:41.000Z","msg":"恭喜恭喜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a140196a96b49f307d309411aae9c99ace7d2402","tid":99104,"uid":45128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T03:34:00.000Z","msg":"失聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"177bdd474f3797bdc9578d285404098dd2df98a9","tid":99104,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T03:35:44.000Z","msg":"去大陸開間保險公司，然後個客出國失蹤賠錢，合法走資<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e368e699d4f0a628f3fac8a0741d9408bef4